      "description": "Presenting an enthusiast-grade E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis has been vetted with documented rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the platform's primary structural concern. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve adjustment and VANOS system overhaul. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, offering precise turn-in and mechanical grip. A mechanically honest example that balances raw performance with legendary E46 ergonomics.",
